baseLang: I'm Black Flying Squirrel from Super Ninja Squadron Koga.

targetLang: みんな覚えててくれてすっごくうれしい~!
baseLang: I'm so happy to hear that everyone remembers me.

targetLang: 今日はあたし一人しかいないけどいつものいくわよ~!
baseLang: I'm the only one here today, but get ready for our usual callout.

targetLang: “五人の忍びがそろうとき誰にも知られず悪を断つ!”
baseLang: "When the five super ninjas unite, they kill evildoers, leaving no trace!

targetLang: “五つの鐘が鳴ったとき悪の響きも聞き納め”
baseLang: When five bells ring, time's up for the evildoers.

targetLang: “コーガはどこでもはせ参上”
baseLang: Koga will go anywhere

targetLang: 〝善悪の彼岸!善悪の彼岸!〞
baseLang: beyond good and evil!"

targetLang: (島田)あっという間に時間が過ぎてしまいました
baseLang: Can you believe today's show is almost over?

targetLang: ムササビさんお別れの前に大切な友人にメッセージを送りたいとか
baseLang: Flying Squirrel wants to send a message to his dear friend.

targetLang: (コウちゃん)公共の電波使って言っちゃうわ
baseLang: I will send out a personal message through the radio.

targetLang: あたしは今の自分も昔の自分も大好き
baseLang: I love who I am, as well as who I was.

targetLang: ひとに何言われようがあたしはあたし
baseLang: No matter what others say about me, I don't care. This is who I am.

targetLang: 昔よりちょっとずうずうしくなったかもしれないけど
baseLang: I may have a thicker skin now than I had then...

targetLang: でも...
baseLang: That said...

targetLang: 気にかけてくれてありがとね
baseLang: I appreciate the fact... that you care about me.

targetLang: ホントにありがと
baseLang: I want to thank you sincerely.

targetLang: (島田)また来てくださいねムササビさん
baseLang: Please come again, Flying Squirrel.

targetLang: それではまた来週おやすみなさい
baseLang: Until next week. Good night, everyone.

targetLang: すいません気付かなくて
baseLang: I'm sorry. I didn't see you.

targetLang: どちらまでご利用ですか?
baseLang: Where are you going?

targetLang: (マスター)はいお待ち
baseLang: Here you go.

targetLang: 6人目の忍び“純白の島ちゃん”です
baseLang: I'm the sixth Super Ninja, White Shima-chan.

targetLang: 僕のお薦めはやっぱり麺入りです
baseLang: My favorite item is "with noodles" after all.

targetLang: 新入りさんコソコソしない
baseLang: Hey rookie, no whispering.

targetLang: かしこまり!
baseLang: Yes, ma'am.

targetLang: それでは皆さん
baseLang: Attention please, everyone.

targetLang: (一同)おやすみなさい!
baseLang: Good night.
